SECTION 01
Module Architecture
The platform is designed as a set of independently deployable, loosely coupled modules. Each module owns its data domain and exposes a defined API surface. Tenants configure which modules are active and how they interconnect through the Admin Configuration Layer. No module is hardwired to another at the code level.
 
