M-03/M-04 (corporate KYB + UBO), M-05/M-06 (CDD/EDD differentiation), M-08 (5-dimension scoring with configurable weights), M-14 (periodic review), M-07 (adverse media + PEP database), M-11 (multi-stage approval paths), M-15 (workflow builder — full feature). Covers: corporate onboarding and risk-differentiated CDD/EDD.
Phase 3 — Enterprise Scale (Months 9-12)
ML-assisted risk scoring, video KYC, blockchain address screening, cross-border transfer orchestration, advanced analytics, bulk management tools, registry API integrations, mobile SDK, white-label deployment framework. Covers: enterprise clients, complex structures, advanced operational maturity.
 
